#

Savory Tuna Avocado Toast

10 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

FishGluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyEasy

Description

A deliciously creamy and savory toast topped with tuna and avocado, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • cherry tomatoes: 5, halved
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
